text: Hey Sahra, hahahaha. Oh, they were so sweet to get me that mother duck t-shirt. How is the statisitical report going?

It’s going alright so far ahaha just wish I was animating instead. The topic is a little depressing. Did you know that full time Japanese animators in their 20’s make as little as $10,500 a year? Animators in their 30’s make around $22,500 and 40s make $31,000. Their working hours are really crazy as well. They work a 6 day week with 10 hours per day. Some have died from exhaustion and some committed suicide after clocking 600 hours of work a month. It’s so sad :disappointed:
